reviewText: I wanted to teach my Introduction to Computer Science class a little coding. This was perfect!  It eveven made them laugh at the outdated jokes!

Well I just learned basic HTML code in a matter of mins.and it makes sense. Looking forward to moving on to more. This is a good DVD if you are looking for the basics. It doesn't let you down; I just wish there was more of it. I purchased this from: From BEAUTY BOUTIQUE ETC here at Amazon. I got it on time and in excellent condition. I would recommend both the seller and the product.
fantastic item shipped as requested, great!  I'm very pleased have a wonderful blessed day John 3:17 filled with lots of smiles :D

Good product. Easy to follow on the TV screen while working on your computer. Makes learning basic html pretty easy. I used it in conjunction with an on ground class and the DVD was easier to follow than the text we used. I had a decent web page up in about 3 days and I goofed off quite a bit. Good product and easier that a book.
I haven't had time to watch it yet.  However, I did receive it in a timely manner.

This video is put together really well. It makes learning HTML very easy for anyone. However, it is also really basic. I was shocked at how much  they didn't cover in the video. If you are just learning how to program  then this is a good start. But if you know the basics already, i would pass  this one up.

I loved this DVD version about learning HTML. It is very easy to  understand and very informative in layman terms. I really enjoyed it  because it also gives you tests. It explains how to do web sites from those  that do all the work for you without the knowledge of HTML tags. This DVD  teaches you to Learn HTML so you can build web sites on your own.
